{"tid":1444251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「文宣」警世 紅毛思想係點","createTime":"2019-08-11T11:54:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T03:57:29.000Z","uid":142332,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f01487f7e622ba17730c951842cf1b45fb1d3231","tid":1444251,"uid":142332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:54:29.000Z","msg":"出自紅底家人：<br />\n<br />\n1.特登拉女仔 費時佢地再比人影到罪證<br />\n保護緊d女仔<br />\n<br />\n2.警察開槍打人合情合理 比我做警察冇得用武力我都唔去做啦<br />\n<br />\n3.宜家就係慢慢唔比你地有言論自由 唔比你地有集會自由<br />\n大陸人唔gur好耐啦 大家都係中國人 憑咩你有特權？<br />\n<br />\n4.d老師反共 所以教到學生都係咁<br />\n<br />\n5.打死班人 殺晒班人<br />\n<br />\n6.特登宜家比警察企係度比你地打 影比全世界睇<br />\n<br />\n7.人地黑社會都識做人 識愛國<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咩意思大家領略啦<br />\n知道對家點洗人腦啦<br />\n知道宜家文宣有咩要補足啦<br />\n<br />\n網絡已經唔夠免費報紙 紅底報紙 同收音機鬥<br />\n<br />\n錢又唔夠<br />\n<br />\n冇嫁啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>if we burn, you burn with us</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nsor...真係好心累 想放個負<br />\n<br />\n如果有第二次批鬥你話幾好"},{"pid":"3004dec8211bd43811073541dc1b7170e9c971b5","tid":1444251,"uid":142332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:54:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca509ee79c5586ad0fc1a9390d55310cf517392b","tid":1444251,"uid":142332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:54:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4d2645aad0878882ba88fec0dd13c992cbbc1d3","tid":1444251,"uid":142332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:54:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ad0a7114678f84a72413deddcb0c4f8b8398e24","tid":1444251,"uid":142332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:55:29.000Z","msg":"好想有日黑警會錯手拉左佢地"},{"pid":"83f4dd5502c341810d0379e03f79da4716597d4d","tid":1444251,"uid":142896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:55:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c15bc4997c30b8ade42eb7d37be20df584c31da6","tid":1444251,"uid":142332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:55:4